      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "128",
        "folderId": "126",
        "text": "Every multistage method with two stages can be defined by four numbers where \n\nk_1 = hf(t_i, u_i)\nk_2 = hf(t_i + c_1 h, u_i + a_11 k_1)\nu_{i+1} = u_i + b_1k_1 + b_2k_2\n\nSee https://fncbook.com/rk/ for more information"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "133",
        "folderId": "126",
        "text": "Here are three methods that are provably convergent. Note that messing with parameters typically leads to divergences of the method, so we need to be very selective with our choices. Can you find any other methods that work?"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "129",
        "folderId": "126",
        "color": "#c74440",
        "latex": "I_{mprovedEuler}\\ =\\ c_{1}\\to\\frac{1}{2},\\ a_{11}\\ \\to\\ \\frac{1}{2},\\ b_{1}\\to0,\\ b_{2}\\to1"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "130",
        "folderId": "126",
        "color": "#2d70b3",
        "latex": "M_{odifiedEuler}\\ =\\ c_{1}\\to1,\\ a_{11}\\ \\to\\ 1,\\ b_{1}\\to\\frac{1}{2},\\ b_{2}\\to\\frac{1}{2}"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "131",
        "folderId": "126",
        "color": "#388c46",
        "latex": "R_{alstonMethod}\\ =\\ c_{1}\\to\\frac{2}{3},\\ a_{11}\\to\\frac{2}{3},\\ b_{1}\\to\\frac{1}{4},\\ b_{2}\\ \\to\\ \\frac{3}{4}"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "151",
        "folderId": "126",
        "color": "#c74440"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "153",
        "folderId": "126",
        "text": "In fact, there is an entire family of two-phrase methods parameterized by \\alpha"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "154",
        "folderId": "126",
        "color": "#388c46",
        "latex": "G_{eneralTwoStep}\\ =\\ c_{1}\\to\\alpha,\\ a_{11}\\to\\alpha,\\ b_{1}\\to1-\\frac{1}{2\\alpha},\\ b_{2}\\ \\to\\ \\frac{1}{2\\alpha}"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "155",
        "folderId": "126",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "\\alpha=0.643",
        "hidden": true,
        "slider": {
          "hardMin": true,
          "hardMax": true,
          "min": "0.000001",
          "max": "1"
        }
      },
